headline: Green Plains Renewable Energy (GPRE) Q4 Earnings Surpass Estimates
summary: Green Plains (GPRE) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +121.64% and -21.91%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
